data.description: This beautiful 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths Jasmine model home is spectular. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, island in kitchen, neutral cabinetry and breakfast bar. Washer and Dryer in unit. Back patio with room for a grill, outdoor dining. and storage closet. Basic cable and internet included in low monthly maintenance. Dog Friendly - 2 allowed, max 35 lbs each. Amenities include clubhouse, fitness center, tennis court, playground and community pool. Fantastic location close to Palm Beach Gardens Mall, Singer Island, John D. MacArthur Beach State Park, I95 and the Turnpike. 15 min drive to downtown WPB and City Place. Townhouse zoned fee simple, FHA allowed!
